{"id":950,"parent_id":949,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":950,"title":"Zechariah 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Zech.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","Zechariah"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Zechariah calls upon Judah to repent—He is shown in vision that the cities of Judah and the temple will be rebuilt."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.1","order":"02.39.001.62737"},["b","1"],"In the eighth month, in the second year of Darius, came the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Zechariah"],", the son of Berechiah, the son of Iddo the prophet, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.2","order":"02.39.001.62738"},["b","2"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath been sore displeased with your fathers."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.3","order":"02.39.001.62739"},["b","3"],"Therefore say thou unto them, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts;",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Turn"],"ye unto me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, and I will turn unto you, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.4","order":"02.39.001.62740"},["b","4"],"Be ye not as your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"fathers"],", unto whom the former prophets have cried, saying, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; Turn ye now from your evil ways, and",["i","from"],"your evil doings: but they did",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"not hear"],", nor",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"hearken"],"unto me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.5","order":"02.39.001.62741"},["b","5"],"Your fathers, where",["i","are"],"they? and the prophets, do they live for ever?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.6","order":"02.39.001.62742"},["b","6"],"But my words and my statutes, which I commanded my servants the prophets, did they not take hold of your fathers? and they returned and said, Like as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"thought"],"to do unto us, according to our ways, and according to our doings, so hath he dealt with us."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.7","order":"02.39.001.62743"},["b","7"],"¶Upon the four and twentieth day of the eleventh month, which",["i","is"],"the month Sebat, in the second year of Darius, came the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"unto Zechariah, the son of Berechiah, the son of Iddo the prophet, saying,"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.8","order":"02.39.001.62744"},["b","8"],"I saw by night, and behold a man riding upon a red horse, and he stood among the myrtle trees that",["i","were"],"in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"bottom"],"; and behind him",["i","were there"],"red horses, speckled, and white."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.9","order":"02.39.001.62745"},["b","9"],"Then said I, O my lord, what",["i","are"],"these? And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"angel"],"that talked with me said unto me, I will shew thee what these",["i","be."]],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.10","order":"02.39.001.62746"},["b","10"],"And the man that stood among the myrtle trees answered and said, These",["i","are they"],"whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath sent to walk to and fro through the earth."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.11","order":"02.39.001.62747"},["b","11"],"And they answered the angel of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that stood among the myrtle trees, and said, We have walked to and fro through the earth, and, behold, all the earth sitteth still, and is at rest."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.12","order":"02.39.001.62748"},["b","12"],"¶Then the angel of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"answered and said, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, how long wilt thou not have mercy on Jerusalem and on the cities of Judah, against which thou hast had indignation these threescore and ten years?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.13","order":"02.39.001.62749"},["b","13"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"answered the angel that talked with me",["i","with"],"good words",["i","and"],"comfortable words."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.14","order":"02.39.001.62750"},["b","14"],"So the angel that communed with me said unto me, Cry thou, saying, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; I am",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"jealous"],"for Jerusalem and for Zion with a great jealousy."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.15","order":"02.39.001.62751"},["b","15"],"And I am very sore displeased with the heathen",["i","that are"],"at ease: for I was but a little displeased, and they helped forward the affliction."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.16","order":"02.39.001.62752"},["b","16"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; I am returned to Jerusalem with mercies: my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"house"],"shall be built in it, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, and a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"line"],"shall be stretched forth upon Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.17","order":"02.39.001.62753"},["b","17"],"Cry yet, saying, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; My cities through prosperity shall yet be spread abroad; and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall yet",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"comfort"],"Zion, and shall yet",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"choose"],"Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.18","order":"02.39.001.62754"},["b","18"],"¶Then lifted I up mine eyes, and saw, and behold four horns."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.19","order":"02.39.001.62755"},["b","19"],"And I said unto the angel that talked with me, What",["i","be"],"these? And he answered me, These",["i","are"],"the horns which have scattered Judah, Israel, and Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.20","order":"02.39.001.62756"},["b","20"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shewed me four",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"carpenters"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.21","order":"02.39.001.62757"},["b","21"],"Then said I, What come these to do? And he spake, saying, These",["i","are"],"the horns which have scattered Judah, so that no man did lift up his head: but these are come to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"fray"],"them, to cast out the horns of the Gentiles, which lifted up",["i","their"],"horn over the land of Judah to scatter it."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.1a","order":"02.39.001.62758"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/5.1"},"Ezra 5:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.3a","order":"02.39.001.62760"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.63"},"D&C 88:63"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"TG Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.4a","order":"02.39.001.62762"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/78.8"},"Ps. 78:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.4b","order":"02.39.001.62764"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.5"},"2 Ne. 27:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.14"},"Jacob 4:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.36"},"D&C 136:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.4c","order":"02.39.001.62766"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.6a","order":"02.39.001.62768"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.17"},"Lam. 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.8a","order":"02.39.001.62770"},["b","8a"],["span.small","IE"],"of the valley."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.9a","order":"02.39.001.62772"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.14a","order":"02.39.001.62774"},["b","14a"],["span.small","HEB"],"zealous.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.18"},"Joel 2:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/8.2"},"Zech. 8:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.16a","order":"02.39.001.62776"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/last-days"},"TG Last Days"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temple"},"Temple"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.16b","order":"02.39.001.62778"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/31.39"},"Jer. 31:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.17a","order":"02.39.001.62780"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/51.3"},"Isa. 51:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.17b","order":"02.39.001.62782"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.1"},"Isa. 14:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.20a","order":"02.39.001.62784"},["b","20a"],["span.small","HEB"],"craftsmen or artisans."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.21a","order":"02.39.001.62786"},["b","21a"],["span.small","HEB"],"terrify."]]}
